客户和供应商的“一周”抉择。
A "one-week" choice between customers and suppliers.
杜涛2020-02-11 13:42。
Tao 2020-02-11 13: 42.
扫描二维码分享到朋友圈。
Scanning two-dimensional code to share with friends.
经济观察网 记者 杜涛一周时间！。
The economic observation network reporter Du Tao one week!
这是广东某地一家制造业的管理者阿蓝的时间表，这是他的客户给他的时间，也是他给上游供应商的时间。
This is the schedule of A Blue, a manufacturer in a part of Guangdong, which is the time his client gives him and the time he gives upstream suppliers.
。
.
2月10日，阿蓝在接受经济观察网采访时表示，现在是一手抓防治（防治新冠肺炎疫情），一手抓生产。
In an interview with the Economic Watch on Feb. 10, Allen said it was time to focus on prevention and treatment (fighting the outbreak of pneumonia in the New Crown) and on production.
防治出现问题，政府问责。
Governments are accountable when problems arise.
生产出现问题，订单没了。
There's a production problem. The order's gone.
订单没了的话，还要供应商干嘛？。
If the order is gone, what else would the supplier do?
一。
One.
阿蓝的工厂现在回来了大约60%的工人，但是不能够完全上岗，上岗的只有几百名在公司当地过年的工人。
Blue's factory is now home to about 60% of workers, but it isn't fully staffed by just a few hundred local workers.
“外地回来的工人，首先要隔离，然后才能上班。
"Workers who return from other places must first be isolated before they can go to work.
”。
"
虽然面临着很大得用工问题，但是也不敢社会招聘，万一出现问题怎么办？。
Although the face of a large number of employment problems, but also afraid of social recruitment, in the event of problems?
即便这样，阿蓝还是面临两个问题。
Even so, Allan faces two problems.
。
.
第一就是口罩不够，虽然现在已经储备了能用一个月的口罩，但是接下来还需要口罩，因为不知道疫情延续到什么时候。
The first is the lack of masks, although there is now a month to use a mask, but the next need for masks, because do not know when the epidemic will continue.
而且现在口罩比较贵，十元一个，在车间使用，一个一戴就是一天。
And now more expensive masks, 10 yuan a, used in the workshop, a day is a wear.
其次便是，即使阿蓝所在公司复工了，但是他们供应商还没有复工，对他们有一定的影响，比如材料供应商，加工供应商。
Second, even if the company is back to work, but their suppliers have not returned to work, they have a certain impact on them, such as material suppliers, processing suppliers.
。
.
阿蓝给记者介绍，复工的标准是准备60天的口罩，消毒液、酒精，测温器，隔离观察室等，其中隔离观察室按照10%的比例准备，也就是说有多少工人，按照10%的比例准备出隔离观察室。
A blue told reporters that the standard for returning to work is to prepare 60-day masks, disinfectants, alcohol, thermostats, isolation observation rooms, etc., with the isolation observation rooms prepared at a 10 per cent ratio, that is to say, the number of workers prepared to leave the isolation observation room at 10 per cent.
因为当地政府要求属地管理，社区没有这么多隔离室， 所以就要求工厂自己准备。
Because the local government requires territorial management, the community does not have so many isolation rooms, so the factory itself is required to prepare.
“这些会增加企业的成本，虽然当地一些扶持政策，但是和企业的损失来看，政策弥补的都是一小部分。
"These add to the cost of doing business, and while there are some local support policies, they are only a small part of what companies lose."
”阿蓝给记者坦言，现在是我们的客户催促我们，我们催促催促我们的供应商。
Alan told reporters that it was our customers who were urging us, and we were urging our suppliers.
供应商回应，一部分人出不来一部分不愿意出来。
Supplier response, some people can not get out of the part unwilling to come out.
。
.
据阿蓝了解，企业复工，政府优先批准一些骨干企业，各个地方政府对于一些小企业复工的审批排的比较靠后。
According to A Lan, the company returned to work, the government gave priority to a number of key enterprises, each local government for some small enterprises to resume work approval platoon is relatively low.
这样就影响整个供应链。
This affects the entire supply chain.
毕竟现在都是细分产业链，不可能一个企业将所有环节都自己生产。
After all, is now a subdivision of the industrial chain, it is not possible for an enterprise to all links of their own production.
。
.
更让阿蓝担心的是国外的一些订单，他告诉记者，若是因为疫情无法复工，有些国外订单就会向东南亚等地方转移，这些订单面临的最大问题是订单走了，再回来就不容易了。
Even more worrying for Allen were orders from abroad, which he told reporters would be diverted to places such as Southeast Asia if the outbreak did not resume. The biggest problem with these orders is that they leave, and it's not easy to come back.
所以现在生产用的都是年前的一些备料和原材料，但是支持不了太久。
So now the production is using some of the year before the material and raw materials, but will not support for long.
。
.
阿蓝透露，他们的客户有一家是国内的电子产品龙头企业，2月1日就不断要求他们赶紧回复生产，但是阿蓝一直拖到了现在，不能再拖了。
One of their customers, a leading electronics company in the country, was demanding a quick return to production on Feb. 1, Allan said, but she couldn't hold off until now.
若是复工时间拖的太长，订单那边可能就没了，我们也会取消供应商。
If the rework time is too long, the order side may be gone, and we will cancel the supplier.
所以一周之内生产，这是订单给我们的时间，也是我们给供应商的时间，不行就要换了，订单都没了，还要供应商干嘛？。
So within a week of production, this is the order given to us, and we give the time to suppliers, can not be changed, orders have been lost, suppliers do?
而关于财务压力，阿蓝告诉记者，账上还有一个多亿，主要面临的就是马上要给上游结账，三个月一结。
Regarding the financial pressure, A Lan told reporters that there is more than a billion on the account, the main face is to pay the bill upstream, three months.
。
.
二。
II.
相比阿蓝，阿黄这边的工厂在前几天就复工生产的申请交到了当地的劳动部门。
Compared with A Lan, the factory on this side of Huang in the last few days on the resumption of production applications to the local labor department.
与阿蓝相同的是，屁股后面一堆订单在追着。
Just like Allan, a bunch of orders were chasing after him.
阿黄的企业主要给一些大的新能源汽车做供应商。
Huang's enterprises mainly to a number of large new energy vehicles as suppliers.
。
.
“刚过完年就一直电话追着问什么时候恢复生产？现在面临着两难的境地，一方面安抚客户，一方面催促上游供应商供货。
"After the New Year, I was on the phone asking when production would resume and faced a dilemma in trying to placate customers while urging upstream suppliers to deliver.
就算安抚住客户，但是信用也要大打折扣了。
Even if the customer is safe, but credit has to be greatly reduced.
”。
"
阿黄所在的地方，在上周末出台了企业若是回复生产，需要政府审批的要求，在要求出台的当天，阿黄便提交了回复生产的申请。
Huang's place, in the weekend to return to production if enterprises need government approval requirements, in the day of the request, Huang submitted a request to resume production.
“我现在做得就是两件事，第一个是新冠防治工作，第二个是为回复生产做的准备工作。
"I am doing two things, the first is the new crown control, the second is the preparation for the resumption of production.
向地方的部门申请递交了很多资料，内部的防控措施，还有内部管理的方案， 等着各个管理部门审批。
Applications to local departments have been submitted, internal control measures and internally managed programmes are pending approval by the respective authorities.
”。
"
而据阿黄了解，审批之前政府部门还要现场检查，检查口罩、防控措施是否到位，然后在决定是否批准。
But according to Huang, before the approval of government departments also on-site inspection, check masks, control measures in place, and then decide whether to approve.
。
.
按照目前政府的要求，阿黄的公司做了很多防范的规章制度，与阿蓝相比幸运的是，阿黄这边员工大部分都是湖南，江西 ，湖北比较少。
In accordance with the current government requirements, Huang's company made a lot of defense regulations, compared with A Lan Fortunately, most of the employees on this side of Hunan, Jiangxi, Hubei are relatively few.
。
.
阿黄告诉记者，公司现在回来了一百多个员工，外地回来的都在隔离，还有没有回去过年的几十名工人可以直接投入生产。
Huang told reporters that the company is now back more than 100 employees, the field back in isolation, there are dozens of workers who have not returned to the New Year can be directly into production.
并且现在所有的员工都封闭在工厂，不准出去，有生活要求都是公司行政部安排。
And now all the employees are closed in the factory, not allowed to go out, there are living requirements are arranged by the company's administrative department.
。
.
据阿黄了解，他的供应商们也在给当地的政府打报告，要求申请恢复生产，但是现在还没有通过。
According to Huang, his suppliers are also reporting to the local government, requesting a resumption of production, but have not yet passed.
。
.
阿黄与阿蓝面临的局面几乎雷同，客户追着打电话要求他们回复生产，他们再去追着供应商恢复生产。
Huang and A Lan face a situation almost identical, customer calls to ask them to return to production, they go after the supplier to resume production.
2月10日，诸多省份迎来了复工首日，但部分地方的企业要正常复工，需要等待地方政府验收后的开工“批文”。
February 10, many provinces ushered in the first day of work, but some local enterprises to resume normal work, need to wait for the local government after acceptance of the start of "approval."
阿黄原计划也是2月10日开工，但是政府回复生产的通知还没下来，也就没有开工。
Mr Aberdeen plans to begin work on February 10, but the government has yet to return to production, so it has not begun.
。
.
“不敢私底下开工呀，在网上看到拘留提前复工企业负责人的新闻，现在能做的就是等着政府的审批下来。
"Do not dare to work in private ah, on the Internet to see the detention of the early resumption of business leaders news, can now do is waiting for the government's approval.
但是现在就2月10日了，在不批准，2月就过去了。
But now, February 10th, in the absence of approval, February passed.
”阿黄有些着急。
Huang was worried.
。
.
国家也已经看到地方政府为企业恢复生产设置的各类条件，2月11日，国务院应对新型冠状病毒感染肺炎疫情联防联控机制举行新闻发布会上，国家发展改革委社会发展司司长欧晓理回应记者提问表示，在防控期间，很多地方都出台了很严格的限制人员进出措施。
On February 11, the State Council held a press conference on the joint control mechanism for the new coronavirus infection with pneumonia. In response to a question from reporters, Xiao Li, director of the social development department of the National Development and Reform Commission, said that during the prevention and control period, many places have put in place strict measures to restrict the entry and exit of people.
比如，有的地方还对企业的复工复产采取了报备制度，有的设置了前置审批条件，甚至还有个别地方出现了拘留提前复工企业负责人的情况。
For example, some places have adopted a reporting system for the resumption of work by enterprises, some have set pre-conditions for approval, and some have even seen the detention of persons responsible for the early resumption of work.
这些做法是不符合加强疫情科学防控、有序做好企业复工复产的中央精神的。
These measures are not in line with strengthening the scientific control of the epidemic, orderly do a good job enterprises to resume production of the central spirit.
此风不可涨。
The wind cannot rise.
在这里明确和大家说，我们将严格制止以审批等简单粗暴方式限制企业复工复产的做法。
In this clear and everyone said, we will strictly stop the approval and other simple rough way to limit the resumption of business operations.
。
.
（应采访对象要求：阿蓝、阿黄为化名）。
(At the request of the interviewee: Alan, Huang for alias).
